question: where did the russian japanese war happen
sparql:
PREFIX ns: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?x
WHERE {
FILTER (?x != ns:m.0c4gf)
FILTER (!isLiteral(?x) OR lang(?x) = '' OR langMatches(lang(?x), 'en'))
ns:m.0c4gf ns:time.event.locations ?x .
}
logical_form: ( JOIN ( R [ time , event , locations ] ) [ Russo-Japanese War ] )

reasoning_information.path_LF: ( JOIN ( R [ time , event , locations ] ) [ Russo-Japanese War ] )
reasoning_information.decomposed: What is the locations of event Russo-Japanese War?
